{"tid":1702150,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Taylor Swift聽日去支那表演 溫提佢唔好提8964/新疆/西藏/香港 唔是會被人bam","createTime":"2019-11-09T14:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T20:32:55.000Z","uid":4322,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"cea811a2b3f82dff058f728a4ca069c608f9bd40","tid":1702150,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"［國際緊急］Taylor Swift 聽晚上天貓雙11 有無人知佢點睇香港？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1701823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1701823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n見到有手足呢個post 我就諗到點玩野好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入去以下佢既social media (fb/ig/tw) 玩野<br />\n一開波祝佢good show先<br />\n之後話你係佢big fan <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最後溫提TS唔好亂講野 千萬唔好提8964/人權/香港示威/新疆集中營/西藏獨立</span></strong></span><br />\n否則CCP會嬲豬 下次無得再去架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(真心唔好屌佢 曲線咁講效果更好 just like South Park道歉!) <br />\n<br />\nSuggested comment flow: <br />\nI am a big fan of you since... &lt;&mdash;-扮fans 打埋幾時開始鍾意<br />\nGood show in china tmr! &lt;&mdash;-基本禮貌 佢唔是仇人<br />\ndon&rsquo;t say anything CCP don&rsquo;t like, <br />\ne.g. 8964, human right, protests in HK, concentration camp in XinJiang and Tibetan independence movement &lt;&mdash; 隨你講幾多野<br />\nthere is censorship in china, you would be banned like South Park if you say sth they don&rsquo;t like... &lt;&mdash;-提佢會畀人ban 抽埋SP<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/taylorswift13\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftaylorswift13&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=e4931528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/taylorswift13</a> (有字數限制但可post圖)<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/taylorswift?igshid=1jqtag3gk0zb8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ftaylorswift%3Figshid%3D1jqtag3gk0zb8&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=a3e63853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/taylorswift?igshid=1jqtag3gk0zb8</a> (無字數限制但唔可以post圖)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/TaylorSwift/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FTaylorSwift%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=7837db46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/TaylorSwift/</a> (無字數限制但唔可以post圖)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tJqt45d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtJqt45d.jpg&h=81a49a7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家入去玩了！"},{"pid":"31d985f42fdc1725d472d631eeeac648f1a67051","tid":1702150,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"535026f9d64435d3488708169d194a4cd36ac5dd","tid":1702150,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"f43cc9f2abd562d011c53f64ba18fe8701cb9839","tid":1702150,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:18:26.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"3467cf7c945364a39b42eeb4aec2834f90f7f330","tid":1702150,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2604de8e2ea2f6916c6ecc2acdc35a0df47dfef1","tid":1702150,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b789f9ba7258dbf902aadf039d401aaeb4e5ec7b","tid":1702150,"uid":87588,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:27:03.000Z","msg":"推到Taylor Swift放棄美國國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"